<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布十分确定阿拉丁就是他要找的男孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他伸出长臂，在孩子群里抓住了阿拉丁的袖子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26572</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快过来，”他说，“你是不是穷裁缝的儿子？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44949</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，”阿拉丁说，“但是我的爸爸几年前就去世了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44950</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49559</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他去世了？”马格里布大声问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49560</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>随着一声呻吟，他双臂抱住阿拉丁的脖子，开始哭泣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么哭呀？”阿拉丁问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的双眼充满了惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63965</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66831</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你认识我爸爸吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66832</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你问我认不认识你爸爸？”马格里布大声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是你爸爸的亲兄弟呀！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在你居然告诉我他死了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>眼泪从他的脸颊流了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86221</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90331</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我叫马格里布，是你的伯父。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90332</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我穿越沙漠，翻过大山过来见他，但是已经太迟了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，”阿拉丁说，“爸爸从来没有提起过您。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117478</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在我看到你的那一刻，我就知道你是我的侄子了。”马格里布低沉地说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117479</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124789</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他依然哭着说：“你长得跟他一模一样。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这英俊的鼻子！这黑黑的眼睛！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134143</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布把阿拉丁抱得更紧了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134144</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139764</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，我的孩子，我应该接受上天的旨意。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139765</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “只要你——我的侄子——还好好地活着就心满意足了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快告诉我，你住在哪里？你妈妈在哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁带着马格里布来到一条街。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>街两边都是歪歪斜斜的房子，房子主要都是用泥和木头盖成的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们家就在这条街的尽头。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180082</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布没有直接过去，他从袖子里拿出了五个金币。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180083</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189280</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快去，”马格里布说，“把这些钱给你妈妈，告诉她你伯父来过。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189281</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今晚我会去你们家，让你妈妈准备好晚餐。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203546</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一定按您说的办，伯父！”阿拉丁看着手里的金币，高兴地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203547</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207809</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从来没有见过这么多钱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207810</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212247</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用最快的速度跑回了家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁到家时，他的妈妈正在忙着纺纱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看到自己的孩子非常惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“除了吃饭时间，我从来都没见过你。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229880</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“晚饭还早着呢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229881</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233663</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你来找我是想要什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233664</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈！”阿拉丁喊道，“好消息！伯父让我代他向你问好！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“伯父？”泽巴问，“你没有伯父啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253810</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈你听我说，”阿拉丁说，“是真的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253811</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁把事情的经过和马格里布的话全部告诉了妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他把金币给了妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267551</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>金币在妈妈的手中发着光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276356</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你爸爸从来没有提起过有个兄弟。”她说，“这真的可能吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然了，妈妈。”阿拉丁说，“伯父还说今晚会来和我们一起吃晚饭！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今晚！”泽巴大声说，“我得马上准备了！需要做的事情太多了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁的妈妈带上金币，赶往市场。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299361</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她买了橄榄油，奶酪，还有一只丰满多肉的小鸡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>回到家，她拿出了最好的餐具，铺上一块色彩鲜艳的餐桌布。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318744</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她烤了面包，炒了一些杏仁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318745</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>晚饭终于准备好了，但是马格里布还没有到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327057</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>331808</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，他在哪里呢？”泽巴问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>331809</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>337452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他有可能迷路了。”阿拉丁说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>337453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>342643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“迷路？”妈妈说，“也许你是对的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>342644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>347512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快跑到路的拐角那边找找他！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>347513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>355518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，他们听到一阵敲门声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>